item.title: Installation
item.description: To install Qurl the most easy way is to use the golang tooling and execute the following: $ go get install github.com/repejota/qurl If you have already installed a previous version of Qurl, you can upgrade it using the -u flag like this: $ go get -u install github.com/repejota/qurl Building from sources If you want to get the latest version or execute the development version of Qurl you can build it from sources:
